{'text': "\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\npnas201211179 1440..1445\n\n\nSee discussions, stats, and author profiles for this publication at: https://www.researchgate.net/publication/234098410\n\nLRP-6 is co-receptor for multiple fibrogenic pathways in pericytes and\n\nmyofibroblasts that are inhibited by DKK-1\n\nArticle\xa0\xa0in\xa0\xa0Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences · January 2013\n\nDOI: 10.1073/pnas.1211179110\xa0·\xa0Source: PubMed\n\nCITATIONS\n\n145\nREADS\n\n255\n\n11 authors, including:\n\nSome of the authors of this publication are also working on these related projects:\n\nMechanisms of fibrosis View project\n\nRetinal Ganglion Cells (RGCs) in Development of the Visual System View project\n\nKathryn Davidson\n\nMonash University (Australia)\n\n24 PUBLICATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa0901 CITATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa0\n\nSEE PROFILE\n\nRichard A Lang\n\nCincinnati Children's Hospital Medical Center\n\n206 PUBLICATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa018,349 CITATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa0\n\nSEE PROFILE\n\nRandall T Moon\n\nUniversity of Washington Seattle\n\n344 PUBLICATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa051,987 CITATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa0\n\nSEE PROFILE\n\nJeremy S Duffield\n\nUniversity of Washington Seattle\n\n172 PUBLICATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa015,013 CITATIONS\xa0\xa0\xa0\n\nSEE PROFILE\n\nAll content following this page was uploaded by Richard A Lang on 16 June 2016.\n\nThe user has requested enhancement of the downloaded file.\n\nhttps://www.researchgate.net/publication/234098410_LRP-6_is_co-receptor_for_multiple_fibrogenic_pathways_in_pericytes_and_myofibroblasts_that_are_inhibited_by_DKK-1?enrichId=rgreq-31f70395118b14f07bc2a00f99ca1a02-XXX&enrichSource=Y292ZXJQYWdlOzIzNDA5ODQxMDtBUzozNzM1ODExMzQ0ODM0NTdAMTQ2NjA4MDA5MTU2Mg%3D%3D&el=1_x_2&_esc=publicationCoverPdf\nhttps://www.researchgate.net/publication/234098410_LRP-6_is_co-receptor_for_multiple_fibrogenic_pathways_in_pericytes_and_myofibroblasts_that_are_inhibited_by_DKK-1?enrichId=rgreq-31f70395118b14f07bc2a00f9